<me>
    M_{\theta}=\begin{bmatrix}
\frac{\sqrt{2}}{2} \amp  -\frac{\sqrt{2}}{2}\\
\frac{\sqrt{2}}{2} \amp  \frac{\sqrt{2}}{2}
\end{bmatrix}.
</me>
